<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
Bumba (feminine) is taken from Brazilian theatrical folk tradition of the popular festival called 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Boi-bumbá">Boi-bumba</normalizedToken>
(hit my bull), which takes place annually in North and Northeastern Brazil.
</paragraph>
